  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0358eca1d351f540a61dc689202b2b8, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "Capitaine, j\u2019ai eu notre client \xE0 la radio !"
    - "Il exige qu\u2019on livre notre marchandise plus t\xF4t que pr\xE9vu, il y
      a eu un probl\xE8me avec le transporteur."
  - <Npc>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c468415a02cbf74438a48816b0fe1fa6, type: 2}
    <Expression>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3973df86522e4b743879172e3518e737, type: 2}
    <Text>k__BackingField:
    - "J\u2019ai essay\xE9 de lui dire qu\u2019on ne pouvait pas, mais il n\u2019a
      rien voulu entendre !"
    - "Je n\u2019ai jamais vu quelqu\u2019un d\u2019aussi t\xEAtu."
